### Health check (public)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Register a new user (always created with role "user")
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo",
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

###

### Login as admin (bootstrap account)
# Use the ADMIN_USERNAME / ADMIN_PASSWORD from your .env — do not hardcode them here.
# Copy access_token → use as Bearer in subsequent requests.
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "<YOUR_ADMIN_USERNAME>",
  "password": "<YOUR_ADMIN_PASSWORD>"
}

###

### Login as regular user (the demo account registered above)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

###

### Get own profile (any authenticated user)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/me
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE>

###

### List all users — admin only (use admin token; demo user gets 403)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE>

###

### Promote a user to admin — admin only (set {user_id} to the target's id)
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/2/role
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "admin"
}

###

### List items (any authenticated user)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE>

###

### Create item (any authenticated user)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Widget Pro",
  "price": 19.99
}

###

### Delete item — admin only (demo user gets 403)
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/1
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE>

###

### Refresh access token (use refresh_token from login response)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE>

###

### Logout (revokes both access and refresh tokens)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "<PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE>"
}

###
